sun.security.ec

Class NamedCurve

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.security.spec.ECParameterSpec
      • sun.security.ec.NamedCurve
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.security.spec.AlgorithmParameterSpec

    public final class NamedCurve
extends java.security.spec.ECParameterSpec
    Repository for well-known Elliptic Curve parameters. It is used by both the SunPKCS11 and SunJSSE code.
    Since:
    1.6
